Captain Joe Gallagher aborts twice in a row bringing him to the attention of General Savage. He tells Gallagher he is going to get a crew of malcontents, "a co-pilot who is all thumbs, a navigator who can&#039;t find his feet, a bombardier who could not hit his plate with a fork".
